      "content": "i mean i get the \"variable star\" thing but it feels way more intentional than just physics. it's like everytime i focus on it there's this static in my head. wouldnt it be possible that something big is using that alignment to broadcast something we just cant pick up with normal telescopes? like a high-freq surveillance array or something?",
